{"title":"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit System Expands with Magnetic Stacking Multi-Tool & Mini Utility Knife!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/14/wolf-tooth-components-8-bit-system-expands-with-magnetic-stacking-multi-tool-mini-utility-knife/","date":1634229756000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113449/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Kit-One_1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-274857\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Move over Swiss Army Knives, there’s a new all-in-one tool in town. And unlike many feature-packed multi-tools, the new 8-Bit Mutli-Tool System from Wolf Tooth Components breaks apart to make it easier to use, regardless of the repair.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System stacked\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113509/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_3-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System apart\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113513/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_5-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Designed as an addition to their existing 8-Bit Tool, what’s fascinating about the new tool&nbsp;<em>system</em> is that initially, the 8-Bit tool wasn’t actually designed with the magnetic stackability in mind. Yet somehow, the design team at Wolf Tooth figured out a way to create a system with three different tools that all nest together with a series of magnets and machined pockets and nubs.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113511/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-System-Kit-One_4-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The resulting form factor is easy to slip into a jersey pocket, bag, or tool roll, and super easy to pull apart and put together.</p><h2>8-Bit Pack&nbsp;Pliers</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System original 8 bit tool\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113504/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_7-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System headset adjustment\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113456/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Pack-Pliers_3_Hex-bits_2-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Starting with their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/11/17/wolf-tooth-components-8-bit-pack-pliers-remix-an-already-great-tool-w-more-functions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">excellent 8-Bit Pack Plier multi-tool</a>, WTC already had a 17 function base to build from.</p><h2>Tech Specs</h2><p><strong>17 Functions:</strong> spoke wrench; valve core wrench; flat head #3.5 and Phillips #2 screwdriver bits; 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5, 6, and 8mm hex; and T10, T25 Torx-compatible bits; install and remove master links; clear tire sealant clogs from valve stem; tighten valve stem lock nut</p><p><strong>Weight:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>70g<br><strong>Dimensions:</strong>&nbsp;146mm x 20mm x 9mm<br><strong>Material:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>7075-T6 aluminum handles, CrV tool steel swivel head, S2 tool steel bits<br><strong>Max Torque:<br></strong></p><ul><li>Max torque for 8 mm hex bit&nbsp;–&nbsp;40 Nm</li><li>Max torque for 4, 5, 6 mm hex bits &amp; T25, T30 bits — 20 Nm</li><li>Max torque for all other bits&nbsp;–&nbsp;10 Nm</li></ul><p><strong>Master links are not included<br></strong><strong>Made in the USA</strong></p><h2>8-Bit Chainbreaker + Utility Knife&nbsp;Multi-Tool</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System utility knife\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3-297x297.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3-800x800.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113523/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife_3-125x125.jpg 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>But there were tools that were notably absent, like a chain breaker and tire plugger. That’s where one of the two new additions comes in. The clever design features a swing-out chain tool that is turned by a custom allen wrench.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System chain tool\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113443/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_3_Chainbreaker-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System tire plugger\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113445/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_4_Tire-plug-inserter-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>On the other end of that allen wrench is a forked end that doubles as a tubeless plugger with the tool body as the handle, and the tubeless plug strips nest inside of the handle.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System utility knife\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113441/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Chainbreaker-and-Utility-Knife-Multi-tool_2_Utility-Knife_1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>At the other end of the tool is something we’ve not seen before in a multi-tool: a retractable mini utility knife. There’s even room for extra blade storage inside the handle. What will you use the blade for on a ride? Anything from cutting zip ties, trimming tubeless plugs, opening stubborn food packages, you name it.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14122441/WTC-8-bit-pack-plier-utility-blade.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14122441/WTC-8-bit-pack-plier-utility-blade.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System utility knife blade compatibility\" width=\"614\" height=\"132\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14122441/WTC-8-bit-pack-plier-utility-blade.jpg 614w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14122441/WTC-8-bit-pack-plier-utility-blade-297x64.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14122441/WTC-8-bit-pack-plier-utility-blade-120x26.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\"></a></p><p>Unlike some of the rather useless mini pocket knife blades we’ve seen on multi-tools, this blade is positioned well for safe use, and since it’s replaceable, it will always be sharp as long as the blade is fresh. WTC will sell a pack of 10 replacement blades for $4.95, and 15 replacement tubeless Bacon strips for $9.95. There’s also room in this part of the tool to store a spare valve core which could come in handy.</p><h2>Tech Specs</h2><p><strong>Weight</strong>:&nbsp;&nbsp;71 g</p><div><p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 146mm x 20mm x&nbsp;11mm</p><p><strong>Material</strong>:&nbsp;7075-T6 aluminum</p><p><strong>Includes:</strong>&nbsp;5 Tire plugs, mini utility blade, spare mini utility blade, tire plug inserter/3mm allen key</p><p><strong>Made in the USA</strong></p><h2>8-Bit Tire Lever + Rim Dent Remover&nbsp;Multi-Tool</h2></div><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System tire lever\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113516/Wolf-Tooth_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-Multi-tool_2-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System tire lever\" width=\"1167\" height=\"459\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260.jpg 1167w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260-297x117.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260-800x315.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260-120x47.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113540/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Tire-Lever-and-Rim-Dent-Remover-e1634228462260-768x302.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1167px) 100vw, 1167px\"></a></p><p>Want more? The middle tool doubles as a truly functional plastic tire lever with a reinforced handle and replaceable tip, while the other end is built to function as a dent remover for aluminum rims.</p><div><h2>Tech Specs</h2><p><strong>Weight</strong>:&nbsp;&nbsp;29.5&nbsp;g</p></div><div><p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 146mm x 20mm x 8mm</p><p><strong>Material</strong>:&nbsp;7075-T6 aluminum, high-strength nylon composite lever</p><p><strong>Made in the USA</strong></p><p><strong>Patents Pending</strong></p><h2>How To Use the Tool</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Uy44XUsL4y8?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>There’s a lot going on here, so WTC created this handy how-to video to show how all the different parts are used together.</p><h2>Pricing &amp; Availability</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370.jpg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components 8-Bit mutil-tool System\" width=\"1200\" height=\"726\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370-297x180.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370-800x484.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370-120x73.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14113527/Wolf-Tooth_Studio_8-Bit-Kit-One_1-e1634229076370-768x465.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>There are two options when it comes to purchasing the 8-Bit Mutli-Tool System. If you already own the 8-Bit Pack Pliers ($69.95), then you can purchase the 8-Bit Chainbreaker + Utility Knife ($69.95) and Tire Lever + Rim Dent Remover ($19.95) separately. Or, if you don’t already have part of the system, you can buy the three part kit for $139.95 for a $20 savings. Almost every part of the system is also available as a replacement to keep your tools in working order. Many of the parts and tools are available now.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=ale&amp;pw=147535&amp;mi=18985&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2F8-bit-system%2Fproducts%2F8-bit-chainbreaker-utility-knife-multi-tool&amp;ctc=xid:fr1634230803110cbf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"ugc\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=ale&amp;pw=147535&amp;mi=18985&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2F8-bit-system%2Fproducts%2F8-bit-chainbreaker-utility-knife-multi-tool\" data-ml-id=\"0\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1634230803110cbf\"><em>wolftoothcomponents.com</em></a></p></div></section></article></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"62b9b14f3d5769e361289ab128b0bb561a4c245760f7dcbcdcfba71f0ed6e31d","category":"Cycling"}